These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Game: billiard, bridge, canasta, chess
1. Game:bridge is on the left of Game:billiard##1
2. Food:mango == Game:chess##1
3. Game:canasta is on the right of Game:billiard##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Game:chess##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Game   | bridge  | billiard     | canasta   | chess |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Music-Genre: disco, country, funk, d&b
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. Music-Genre:d&b == Sport:soccer##1
2. Music-Genre:disco is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:country is on the right of Music-Genre:d&b##1
4. Music-Genre:d&b is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | d&b | country | disco    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

