2. Beverage:lemonade == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Beverage:cola##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage         | lemonade | cola | almond-milk   | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

